				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${C}_{{ij}}={C}_{{ji}}$$\end{document}Cij=Cji was given by the number of fibers connecting two brain regions. To have values between 0 and 1, we normalized the weights by dividing them by the largest value, i.e., \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
